reviewText:
To be honest, the biggest negative feeling came the moment instructor's newly created page was banned by Facebook. And the instructor didn't even explain, how to avoid it, or what to do in this situation.
Later during the whole course the instructor was basicaly reading the lables on the buttons without explaining how to use features in the better way. 
I won't recommend spend time on this guided project.

The course had skimmed over the explanation for a lot of features. It would have been better if this course was split into multiple courses, all on "Marketing using FB", with each course focusing on just few topics but in detail.
